Dependencies:
	libev - http://software.schmorp.de/pkg/libev.html

To install libev do the following:
	Gentoo: emerge libev
	Fedora: yum install libev-devel
	Ubuntu: apt-get install libev-devel

Compilation:
	Simply type "make" at the command line.

Configuration:
	Edit "forward.conf" to add additional Port:IP:Port fowarding pairs.
	The format is as such [Port server listens on]:[Remote IP address]:[Remote Port]

Execution:
	Type "./forward-server"
